NFT PFP Idea

November 20, 2021

NFT and Crypto have become incredibly popular. While I am un-sure of the longevity of crypto, I do like some of the technology behind the idea(s). NFTs in particular have given artists a digital outlet to present their work. I enjoy seeing the NFT profile pictures on twitter and some of the incredibly unique ideas people have. I decided to take a stab at a profile picture.
